{"tid":1478441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[開錯台再開過][旗海戰略]係時候出埋歐盟旗","createTime":"2019-08-16T13:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:35:55.000Z","uid":215715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5632fc24d90687add6ea81434291ed652cc0b796","tid":1478441,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:48:45.000Z","msg":"有香港旗 有英國旗 有美國旗 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解冇歐盟旗?</span><br />\n歐盟係第一個對林奠發出最高級別外交照會<br />\n第一個國家收政庇 收黃台仰幫義士著草提供案例<br />\n第一個對香港發出旅遊警示(愛爾蘭)<br />\n出正式聲明仲快過英國 硬過美國 <br />\n係時候多謝歐盟<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">烏克蘭當年廣場革命都係因為歐盟旗<br />\n先令示威者得到大量歐盟國家非戰略物資援助</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.euractiv.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/hungarians_protest_against_orban.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.euractiv.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2015%2F02%2Fhungarians_protest_against_orban.jpeg&h=023f8175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.europeaninterest.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Euromaidan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europeaninterest.eu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FEuromaidan.jpg&h=5517cfea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.vocaleurope.eu/wp-content/uploads/20140203PHT34627_original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vocaleurope.eu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20140203PHT34627_original.jpg&h=f0e81fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.chathamhouse.org/sites/default/files/styles/teaser_800x480/public/images/2017-04-12-Maidan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chathamhouse.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fteaser_800x480%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2017-04-12-Maidan.jpg&h=9b3f67e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/e315r3TiOL51LRSuKs0..g--~B/aD0yMjQxO3c9NDI5NjtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/ap_webfeeds/51a2daf47255ae28440f6a706700e